Description: lightweight tabbed file manager for Linux
 Spin FM is a compact Qt file manager with tabbed navigation, configurable
 themes, drag and drop, freedesktop Trash support, removable USB storage
 controls, selected-item MIME, file-size, and recursive folder-size reporting,
 and an embedded audio player. Long-running file, device, and metadata
 operations run outside the UI thread, while multimedia support is initialized
 on demand.
